reviews.review:
This game is the honest American Dream. They started making money and they invested it right back into the game. I believe they earned every penny too. All of the skins and characters are top quality. Characters are good looking and outfits are cool. A lot of effort was put into the LORE. Things are priced fairly! This is almost unheard of in today's game "industry." The people that worked on this game deserve a round of applause. I have over 1000 hours in this game and I'm amazed every day at the details and thoughtfulness displayed in every detail of the game. A lot of people get distracted with player base toxicity and tend to forget this is a game to be enjoyed. That's why they took the brightness and contrast. There's a decision behind every change and more often than not its the correct decision. I don't know how things work behind the scenes but let me tell you those people have good heads on their shoulders.


tldr;
[b]This game sets a positive example for the game "Industry". [/b]
